column5: A few hours at the Port paid off with this nice 7 lb Brown.  Also wanted to introduce myself.  I've fished since I was a kid but fishing is an ever evolving art and science, so I look forward to learning new techniques and everything else this board has to offer.  I Just a backgrounder: I live near Hamilton, work as a water resources scientist...If it swims I will fish for it!  Cheers
Welcome aboard and congrats on a nice fish.  Mike
Howdy and welcome,  Nice look'n browny...Real round & healthy!
Welcome to the best board the net has to offer. Nice football..ya thats fur shure.
....Welcome Carponthefly. You'll find it can be a bumpy ride at times but we have a vast base of knowledge here when it's needed.
Welcome to the board and nice brownie!
Hey there...nice catch there!!! welcome to the board...you'll find people here are the greatest.
wow that thing sure has been eating!  Cheers!
awesome, super nice brown you got there.  welcome aboard, kemper
welcome aboard my friend and thats a real nice football sized,fat brown...WTG....
Welcome aboard. W2G on the brown trout.    jordan
